ounds-table.test.tsx` —\n1630\t    populated Close Call rendering with the Pyth `expo -8` sublabel, all\n1631\t    twelve column headers, phase + outcome dual chips (open / settled /\n1632\t    refunded × pending / green / red / refund), `title=` audit hover for\n1633\t    long pubkeys, an open-round null-set asserting at least 3 em-dashes\n1634\t    (closePrice + settleTx + settledAt), the refunded+refund composite\n1635\t    refund row, the sparse state pointing at `closecall_rounds`, and the\n1636\t    error-alert state.\n1637\t  - `peek/src/components/__tests__/game-rounds-filter-bar.test.tsx` — the\n1638\t    discriminated-union form. FlipYou + Pot Shot variant: blank-form state\n1639\t    with the `phase` whitelist matching `PEEK_ROUND_PHASES`, populated state\n1640\t    reflecting every filter value back into the input, Pot Shot's aria\n1641\t    label, the missing `Outcome` dropdown (rounds table has no Pyth\n1642\t    outcome), and the `name` attributes aligning with\n1643\t    `normalizeRoundFiltersFromSearchParams`. Close Call variant: phase +\n1644\t    outcome whitelists per `PEEK_CLOSECALL_PHASES` /\n1645\t    `PEEK_CLOSECALL_OUTCOMES`, the missing `High settle attempts` checkbox\n1646\t    (closecall has no `settle_attempts` column), populated state, and the\n1647\t    `outcome` input name contract.\n1648\t  - `peek/src/lib/__tests__/games-search-params.test.ts` —\n1649\t    `normalizeRoundFiltersFromSearchParams`,\n1650\t    `normalizeCloseCallRoundFiltersFromSearchParams`,\n1651\t    `readPageFromSearchParams`, and `buildRoundsQueryString`. Covers\n1652\t    empty / whitespace / undefined / array (Next.js repeated-param) inputs,\n1653\t    the phase + outcome whitelist falling back to `null` instead of\n1654\t    producing a SQL match-nothing filter, the boolean checkbox semantics\n1655\t    (`1`/`true`/`on`/`yes`), the Close Call shape never carrying\n1656\t    `highAttempts` even if the URL passes `stuckAttempts`, page clamping\n1657\t    (`\"\"`,