`).\n1452\t    `PeekCloseCallRoundStuckFilters = Omit<…, 'highAttempts'>` because\n1453\t    `closecall_rounds` has no `settle_attempts` column — the type system\n1454\t    enforces the per-table difference instead of a runtime check.\n1455\t  - `PeekRoundFilters` and `PeekCloseCallRoundFilters` adding\n1456\t    phase/outcome/search/date filters around the stuck struct;\n1457\t    `PeekRoundsListResult<TRow>` couples rows + pagination.\n1458\t- New `peek/src/server/db/queries/get-game-rounds.ts`:\n1459\t  - `listRounds({ sql?, game, filters?, page?, pageSize?, thresholds? })`"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e3ee47e7-eefe-4e12-a068-a08216780c1e","uuid":"bed9e97e-30e0-424d-8b48-e60fb966bc48","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:33:31.844Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/305-peek-operations-admin/history.md","content":"  counters; deferred games (Crash, Game of Trades, Chart the Course, Slots\n  Utopia, Tug of Earn) appear as documented placeholders only, per\n  System Invariant 13.\n- New `peek/app/games/page.tsx` — server-rendered route, `dynamic =\n  \"force-dynamic\"`. Calls `getPeekActorContext` + `isRouteAllowedForRole`\n  for the page-level access gate (the layout already does the outer gate\n  via the `AdminShell`; the page repeats the check so a no-role caller\n  still sees an `<alert>` instead of an empty data shell). Sections:\n  - **Overview** — feeds the 6-metric strip (`games.total_entries`,\n    `games.unique_users`, `games.wagered_lamports`, `games.settled_entries`,\n    `games.refund_entries`, `games.payout_lamports`) into the existing\n    `MetricStrip`. Each metric carries the FR-4 bookkeeping (label,\n    definition, source `game_entries`, window \"All time\", asOf,\n    `freshness: \"live\"`, drilldown `/games`).\n  - **Per-game activity** — renders the new `GamesOverviewTable`\n    against `overview.perGame` (3 rows, one per known `PeekGameId`,\n    zero-filled when missing).\n  - **Deferr